  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">AlleyRoads Project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">IFC expects the Project to increase access to good quality affordable housing in a market characterized by a large demand-supply gap. It will also contribute to job creation, training, and development of supply chains in the local community. Finally, demonstration and replication effects are expected by showcasing that green affordable housing projects in the rental space can be profitable and successful.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Project is to construct and operate 1,061 green affordable housing units for rent across three housing developments in the Greater Johannesburg region (South Africa), over the next three years (the Project).</narrative>
  </description>
